Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.00,0:00:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.63,0:00:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美小姐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.81,0:00:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美身上測出魔族的波動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.68,0:00:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外，別無其他反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.15,0:00:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是最壞的狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.58,0:01:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情...久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.02,0:02:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.44,0:02:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.88,0:03:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仲人先生，不要緊吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.82,0:03:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好，要趕快包紮才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.72,0:03:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊...到底怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.16,0:03:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.96,0:03:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美變成惡魔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.40,0:03:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美又再度進入攻擊狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.67,0:03:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將推進用的ENG能源全部集中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.97,0:03:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將久留美周圍的重力給封鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.91,0:03:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再使久留美的行動變緩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.96,0:04:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊，快清醒過來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.90,0:04:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣，久留美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.42,0:04:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.70,0:05:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力平衡被破壞了，這樣下去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.76,0:05:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.33,0:05:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧?仲人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.37,0:05:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.57,0:05:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為卜占出不祥的卦，過來看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.01,0:05:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果情形真是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.78,0:05:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動力質量故障
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.95,0:05:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法恢復平衡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.25,0:05:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將補助動力的質量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轉到緊急推動裝置上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.62,0:06:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用手動系統保持平衡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.12,0:06:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將著陸的損壞降到最低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.70,0:06:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基地...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.51,0:07:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾小路博士...不要緊吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.58,0:07:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,損壞情況如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.39,0:07:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第16區，能源迴路受損
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.69,0:07:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第8、13區，有不明原因火災
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.30,0:07:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第3、4、5區，也有事故發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.60,0:07:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.74,0:07:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包圍著久留美的防衛罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.87,0:07:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是完整體數據的10%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.68,0:07:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裡面魔族的波動越來越大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.49,0:07:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都講過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.32,0:07:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾小路博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.86,0:07:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何要讓鋼鐵天使們互相戰鬥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.96,0:07:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情原本都是因你而起的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.06,0:07:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直都反對使用禁之力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將魔族給封印，然後將
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.37,0:07:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ANGELHEART
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.77,0:07:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能源升高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.20,0:08:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種理論是沒有問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.11,0:08:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，你看這種狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.28,0:08:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還可以說沒有問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.11,0:08:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有加入緊停止裝置這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.45,0:08:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是怎麼想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.35,0:08:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再固執你那爛理論了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.58,0:08:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你講甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.55,0:08:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停手，現在不是吵架的時候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.89,0:08:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼鐵天使她們也和我們一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.20,0:08:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有顆平常心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.60,0:08:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你卻無視，讓她們互相打鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會使控制ANGEL
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.87,0:08:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HEART的天使本能產生抗拒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.38,0:08:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天使將自己的心給封閉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.18,0:08:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使被壓抑的魔族舒展出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.52,0:08:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後結果就是久留美被惡魔控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.86,0:08:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變成了KAOSANGEL
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.36,0:08:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你講的對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.73,0:08:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是製造出久留美的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.16,0:09:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就需要由我們來負責嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.41,0:09:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.25,0:09:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美的情況如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到目前為止，整體未有變化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.69,0:09:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是魔族的波動還是繼續增強中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.89,0:09:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在目標周圍做出的防衛罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.20,0:09:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經到達完成體數據的50%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.80,0:09:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，繼續監視    遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.61,0:09:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現階段已經到達50%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.58,0:09:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼變成完成體只剩下二個小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.81,0:09:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻不是0
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.48,0:09:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能讓這個世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.08,0:09:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我們一樣遭到不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.22,0:09:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以一定要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.62,0:09:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是失去這ACADEMY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.06,0:10:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看博士他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.40,0:10:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很擔心姊姊現在的情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.83,0:10:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仲人先生先在此休息一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.87,0:10:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡鈴加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.44,0:10:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡鈴加，我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.80,0:10:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒有其他意見了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.58,0:10:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙希  卡鈴加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.75,0:11:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.69,0:11:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在沉睡中，靜靜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.26,0:11:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是當久留美次甦醒的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.50,0:11:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我們的力量就無法抵擋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.00,0:11:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點你們應該也明白吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.07,0:11:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...天城博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.01,0:11:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你們到底想做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.58,0:11:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個選擇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.52,0:11:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將動力移轉倒轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.09,0:11:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用臨界裝置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.16,0:11:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將ACADEMY的全部能源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝向久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.26,0:11:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將裡面存在的東西給消滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.90,0:11:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消滅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.17,0:11:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了準備這計畫...    不可以!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.24,0:11:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以這樣!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.27,0:11:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊...姊姊一定會恢復成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.87,0:11:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前的姊姊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.71,0:11:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.05,0:12:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧?綾小路博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.58,0:12:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定有甚麼辦法吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.89,0:12:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不講話呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.92,0:12:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威路斯基博士，不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.73,0:12:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.43,0:12:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美的防衛罩突然暴增
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.76,0:12:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.20,0:12:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔族的反應也急速增大中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.14,0:12:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能，速度太快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.85,0:12:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「KAOSANGEL」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.41,0:14:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情應該不是這樣子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.28,0:14:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有希望啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.04,0:14:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是久留美只剩下一條路可走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.31,0:14:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.25,0:14:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次回 鋼鐵天使久留美第23話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.69,0:14:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「罪與罰」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.36,0:14:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們到底做了甚麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.89,0:14:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情應該不是這樣子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.50,0:14:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾小路博士，別放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.50,0:14:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定還有希望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.70,0:14:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在某個地方，一定會有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.10,0:14:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是久留美只剩下一條路可走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.07,0:14:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是...   不行，不要講了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.94,0:14:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.41,0:14:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.64,0:14:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次回  鋼鐵天使久留美第23話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.48,0:14:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「罪與罰」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.82,0:14:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是保持房間光亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.09,0:15:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與電視保持距離
